## ðŸŽ§ Speech Emotion Datasets Used

### 1. RAVDESS (Ryerson Audio-Visual Database of Emotional Speech and Song)
Official Link:
https://zenodo.org/records/1188976

Description:
24 professional actors (12 male, 12 female) speaking two statements with 8 emotional classes.

---

### 2. TESS (Toronto Emotional Speech Set)
Official Link:
https://tspace.library.utoronto.ca/handle/1807/24487

Description:
Two female actresses (younger & older) speaking 200+ target words across 7 emotion categories.

---

### 3. CREMA-D (Crowd-Sourced Emotional Multimodal Actors Dataset)
Official Link:
https://github.com/CheyneyComputerScience/CREMA-D

Alternate Link:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ejlok1/cremad

Description:
91 actors (48 male, 43 female) speaking 12 sentences in 6 emotions. Audio & video provided.


